Cut Wrapping Paper Easy & Fast
Just Slide To Get Perfectly Straight Cuts!

If you're sick of cutting your wrapping paper and making not-so-straight cuts, then this Unique Sliding Wrapping Paper Cutter is just what you need! It gives you the power to cut a perfect piece of wrapping paper every time. It also doubles as an organizer for easy storage by perfectly holding it in place so that it won't unravel!

FEATURES:

  • SILKY-SMOOTH CUTS EVERY TIME - This cutter has a razor built into it that easily cuts any type of wrapping paper. Just place it around any tube of wrapping paper and slide it down to cut.
  • FLEXIBLE HINGE - Perfectly holds wrapping paper in place for easy preparation and organization. Can be used on any size roll of paper.
  • SAVES YOU TIME - No more measuring, folding, and double-guessing! Wrap presents in half the time and effort. Just measure how much paper you need, use the sliding paper cutter to cut the paper, and start wrapping!

How To Use:

  1. Slide the device over the wrapping paper.
  2. Pull a sheet of paper through the larger slot in the device.
  3. Once the sheet of paper is the desired length, slide Wrapping Paper Cutter to the end of the roll allowing the paper to drop into the slot where the blade is embedded.
  4. Now gently push Wrapping Paper Cutter forward to cleanly cut the paper.
  5. Once the slice is complete, simply bring Wrapping Paper Cutter back to the center of the wrapping paper.

Introducing: Smart multifunctional handlebar bag

Our minimal and unobtrusive bike mount features an easy on/off latch, and an integrated shoulder strap allows you to take the bag along on every adventure, on or off the bike.

Integrated tech: right where you need it 

The Handlebar Bag features a customizable dashboard that puts your devices at your fingertips. The Tech Mount in the center of the dashboard integrates with adapters for all the most popular cycling computers, GPS units, and even accommodates mobile devices. Check your map, monitor your performance, or skip to your favorite track for the next big climb.  

Instant, one-handed access 

This bag will never slow you down. A secure, spring-loaded latch gives you instant, one-handed access to bag contents while on or off the bike. Grab that granola bar at the top of an ascent, or check your phone while cruising through the neighborhood.  

Easy on/off and integrated strap

The Handlebar Bag is portable and ready for every adventure. Attach or detach instantly with the flip of a lever. When you reach your destination, take the bag along with you using the integrated shoulder strap .   

Minimal and modern 

The Handlebar Bag mounts directly to your handlebars with discreet hardware that's simple to install. The machined aluminum mount is rigid and secure, and anodized for durability. The mount is minimal and unobtrusive so your bike looks great with or without the mount. 

Designed to fit 31.8mm handlebars, the mount may be adapted to smaller bars with widely available shims.

Ready for any ride

We designed The Handlebar Bag with flexible storage for every riding style. From morning commutes to unsupported gravel adventures, our bag offers expandable storage with thoughtful details to securely transport objects large and small.   

Go ahead: bring it all along! 

Two M5 Accessory Mounts on either side of the bag allow you to further free up space on your handlebars. Carry bar-mounted accessories directly on the bag or on a machined aluminum Handlebar Stub.
